name: FoFar
description: A legendary character inspired by Matt Furie's Boy's Club comic. The red mascot of the red chain, TRON. FoFar is a community meme on Tron and the first Matt Furie character on TRX, being the first market mover has given FoFar a great advantage for growth on the Tron Chain. We aim to produce high quality memes and content to tron users, the "Brett" or "Pepe" of Tron. FoFar has had great organic growth and it is not slowing down.
